sub_title: Student at the University of Twente
summary: As a Civil Engineer who studied at the University of Twente I have acquired knowledge and several abilities in the fields of water management, traffic management, and infrastructure management. I've worked on initiatives in these fields with the goal of finding answers while keeping sustainability in mind, additionally I have used several mathematical and simulation models in order to aid these answers.
